     C                   PARM                    @FDNPC2                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDTPE2                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDDAT2                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDNOP2                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDLIN2                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDLOGI                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDORIG                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDEDAU                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDERAV                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDTEXT                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDDATO                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDWAUD                                            
     C                   PARM                    @FDCANT                                            
